more from you.

1044
01:37:13,953 --> 01:37:16,913
I thought you'd be
smarter than this.

1045
01:37:16,998 --> 01:37:20,375
Well, I'm happy
to disappoint you.

1046
01:37:33,973 --> 01:37:36,349
