Four more weeks. Oh, man.

1077
01:39:28,296 --> 01:39:31,506
We've got to get the other
drop ship from the Sulaco.

1078
01:39:31,591 --> 01:39:34,551
I mean, there must be some way
of bringing it down on remote.

1079
