alien back through quarantine...

1199
01:51:55,959 --> 01:51:58,669
if one of us
was impregnated-

1200
01:51:59,963 --> 01:52:02,173
whatever you call it-

1201
01:52:02,257 --> 01:52:04,842
and then frozen
for the trip home.

1202
01:52:04,926 --> 01:52:08,971
