embryos we were carrying-

1203
01:52:09,056 --> 01:52:11,098
me and Newt.

1204
01:52:12,934 --> 01:52:14,894
Wait a minute, now.
We'd all know.

1205
01:52:14,978 --> 01:52:17,229
Yes. The only way
he could do it...

1206
01:52:17,314 --> 01:52:21,067
is if he sabotaged certain
freezers on the way home.

1207
01:52:21,151 --> 01:52:23,736
Namely yours.

