Seventeen meters.

1245
01:54:55,805 --> 01:54:58,182
Something under the floor, not in the plans.
I don't know.

1246
01:54:58,266 --> 01:55:00,351
- Fifteen meters.
- Ripley!

1247
01:55:00,435 --> 01:55:03,938
- Definitely inside the barricades.
- Let's go.

1248
01:55:05,565 --> 01:55:07,441
