Hey.

1402
02:22:42,137 --> 02:22:44,638
We made it.

1403
02:22:44,723 --> 02:22:46,724
I knew you'd come.

1404
02:23:01,656 --> 02:23:03,824
He's gonna be all right.
He's just out.

1405
02:23:03,909 --> 02:23:06,285
I had to give him another shot
for the pain.

1406
02:23:07,495 --> 02:23:10,080
