to carry him up to Medical.

1407
02:23:10,165 --> 02:23:12,166
Okay.

1408
02:23:17,839 --> 02:23:21,842
I'm sorry if I scared you. That
platform wasjust becoming too unstable.

1409
02:23:21,927 --> 02:23:24,720
